title: "An unidentified flying object " is seen as a space rocket explosion?
subtitle: The video capture of the explosion of the Space X-9 Hawk rocket during the test shooting appears to show that an unidentified flying object passes over the rocket just before that.
author: Alex Kasprak
vclaim: An unidentified bird ' s body passes over the Space X 9 Hawk rocket at the same moment that it explodes, suggesting that the missile was deliberately destroyed.
